:"Sprinkle with breadcrumbs and dot with 15 g butter, diced in small pieces, then bake for 12-15 minutes (180°C) until golden."},{"content":"Serve with a salad or vegetables."}],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","45m","6 portions"]}